  "schema:description": "TaskSolution carrying the actual measured metrics from running core_implementation_gemini-2-5-pro.py against the gemini-2.5-pro stable endpoint. CAVEATS: (1) only the control-dependency / trace subtask was run (489 instances from CoRe Lite); data dependency and information flow subtasks were not run and are intentionally omitted. (2) Endpoint mismatch: the paper used gemini-2.5-pro-preview-05-06; this run used the gemini-2.5-pro stable endpoint, so numbers are not directly comparable to Table 4. (3) 15 of 489 instances had API failures (same model, intermittent) and were forced to pred=False; reported F1=80.2 includes those failures. F1 excluding the 15 failures (i.e. over the 474 instances with valid responses) is 82.03. (4) For paper-reported numbers, see ../pdf2ct/core_solution_gemini-2-5-pro_paper.jsonld.",
